---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Sam Gross"
  description="Product management leader helping great teams and great people to do even greater things."
>
  <article class="about-content">
    <h1>About Sam</h1>

    <section class="intro">
      <p class="lead">
        I help great teams and great people to do even greater things.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Current Role</h2>
      <p>
        Product management leader at <strong>Occupier</strong>, based in Washington, D.C., United States.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Background</h2>
      <p>
        My experience spans organizations of varying scales, from major corporations to startups and my own ventures.
        I've had the privilege of working on diverse projects that have shaped my approach to product development and team leadership.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Notable Projects</h2>
      <ul class="projects-list">
        <li>SAMATE project at NIST</li>
        <li>OSCAAR project at University of Maryland</li>
        <li>Apple Store App development</li>
        <li>Hardware and software project management</li>
        <li>IT deployments at corporate level</li>
        <li>Founded and led Technical Product Management at Oscar Insurance</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Interests</h2>
      <p>
        When I'm not building products, you can find me cycling around D.C. or exploring the latest in technology.
        I'm passionate about photography, which you can see throughout this site, and I enjoy sharing my thoughts
        on technology and product development through my blog.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        I'm always interested in connecting with folks working on interesting problems. You can reach me at
        <a href="mailto:sam@samthegeek.net">sam@samthegeek.net</a> or find me on
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/samthegeek" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a> and
        <a href="https://mastodon.social/@SamTheGeek" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mastodon</a> as @SamTheGeek.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>

  <style>
    .about-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #222;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #444;
      margin: 0;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .projects-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .projects-list li {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .projects-list li::before {
      content: "â†’";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    a {
      color: #0066cc;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
      text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }

    a:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .lead {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .intro {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
